author: Seth Herald
title: Trump backers protest Michigan stay-at-home orders at state capitol
description: Thousands of demonstrators in cars with horns honking thronged around Michigan's state Capitol on Wednesday, some chanting "lock her up," to protest against stay-at-home orders imposed by Governor Gretchen Whitmer to stop the coronavirus.
